Supports nullable unique constraints (optional). Ref #43

**Example**
```python
DATABASES = {
    'default': {
        'ENGINE': 'sql_server.pyodbc',
        'NAME': 'mydb',
        'USER': 'user@myserver',             
        'PASSWORD': 'password',
        'HOST': 'myserver.database.windows.net',
        'PORT': '',

        'OPTIONS': {
            'driver': 'ODBC Driver 11 for SQL Server',
            'supports_nullable_unique_constraints': True
        },
    },
}
```

